{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place cream, milk, buttermilk, vanilla bean paste and both milk and dark chocolates into mixing bowl and warm <nobr>5 min\/37°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>, or until chocolate melts."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Add sugar and egg white and cook <nobr>8 min\/90°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Add Frangelico® and blend <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. <strong><strong>Remove butterfly whisk.<\/strong><\/strong> Transfer mixture into shallow freezable containers, up to 4 cm high, or 2 ice cube trays and cover with plastic wrap. Allow mixture to cool completely then place into freezer overnight.","Transfer frozen gelato into refrigerator for 15 minutes, then cut into pieces (4 x 4 cm). Place half of the gelato pieces into mixing bowl and crush <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>, then mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr> with aid of spatula. Transfer into a freezable container.","Place remaining gelato pieces into mixing bowl and crush <nobr>20 sec\/speed 6<\/nobr>, then mix <nobr>10 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr> with aid of spatula. Transfer into freezable container. Return to freezer for another 3-4 hours or until firm. Sprinkle with shaved chocolate (optional) before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["60 g thickened cream","250 g full cream milk","500 g buttermilk","½ tsp vanilla bean paste","70 g milk chocolate, broken into pieces","70 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces, plus extra for shaving (optional)","130 g caster sugar","1 egg white","1 tbsp Frangelico®"]}],"id":"r107028","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-gpErxi01fZI\/XZWc9WnpHYI\/AAAAAAAAehM\/IdyVWpIiJigF434vu-XyRnljCVHhKVJlACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_A6KyMWayIB2iOCYQ.png","title":"Chocolate Frangelico® gelato","publishedAt":"2016-07-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11.3 g","fat":"20.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"65.9 g","calories":"2030 kJ \/ 483 kcal"},"usefulItems":"plastic wrap, freezable storage container, 2 ice cube trays, freezer, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["You can use any creamy liqueur you have available in this recipe. Omit the alcohol to make this a kid-friendly treat."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","28h","4 portions"]}